quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  73,20,"Lalle ne, Ubangijinka Yã sani cẽwa, kai kana tsayuwa a kusan kashi biyu daga uku na dare, da rabinsa, da sulusinsa, tãre da wani ɓangare na waɗanda ke tãre da kai. Allah Yake iya ƙaddara dare da yini, Ya san bã zã ku iya lissafa shi ba, sabõda haka Ya karɓi tubarku sai, ku karanta abin da ya sauƙaƙa na Alƙur'ãni. Ya san wasu daga cikinku, zã su yi cĩwo, kuma wasu zã su yi tafiya cikin ƙasa suna nẽman falalar Allah da fatauci, kuma wasu zã su yi yãƙi a cikin banyar Allah. Sabõda haka ku karanta abin da ya sauƙaƙa daga gare shi, kuma ku tsai da salla kuma ku bãyar da zakka, kumaa ku bai wa Allah rance, rance mai kyãwo. Kuma abin da kuka gabatar dõmin kanku, na alhẽri, zã ku sãme shi a wurin Allah zai kasance mafifici (daga wanda kuka ajiye) kuma zai fi girma ga sakamako, kuma ku rõƙi Allah gãfara; lalle ne Allah Mai gãfara ne, Mai jin ƙai"
  74,1,Yã wanda ya lulluɓa da mayãfi
  74,2,Ka tãshi dõmin ka yi gargaɗi
  74,3,"Kuma Ubangijinka, sai ka girmama Shi"
  74,4,"Kuma tutãfinka, sai ka tsarkake su"
  74,5,"Kuma gumãka, sai ka ƙaurace musu"
  74,6,Kada ka yi kyauta kana nẽman ƙãri
  74,7,Kuma sabõda Ubangijinka? Sai ka yi haƙure
  74,8,"To, idan aka yi bũsa a cikin ƙaho"
  74,9,"To, wannan, a rãnar nan, yini ne mai wuya"
  74,10,"A kan kãfirai, bã mai sauƙi ba ne"
  74,11,"Ka bar Ni da wanda Na halitta, yana shi kaɗai"
  74,12,Kuma Na sanya masa dũkiya shimfiɗaɗɗiya
  74,13,Da ɗiyã halartattu
  74,14,Kuma Na shimfiɗa? masa kõme shimfiɗãwa
  74,15,"Sa'an nan, yanã kwaɗayin in yi masa ƙãri"
  74,16,"Faufau! Lalle ne, shĩ yã kasance, ga ãyõyin Mu, mai tsaurin kai"
  74,17,Zã Ni kallafa masa wahala mai hauhawa